msgstr "Pellgewsewgh gans klapkodh ha SIP"

#: data/org.gnome.Calls.metainfo.xml.in:10
msgid ""
"Calls is a simple, elegant phone dialer and call handler for GNOME. It can "
"be used with a cellular modem for plain old telephone calls as well as VoIP "
"calls using the SIP protocol."
msgstr ""
"Galowyow yw galowyell klapkodh sempel hag afinys, ha handlell galow rag "
"GNOME. Y hyll ev bos devnydhys gans modem kellgowser rag galowyow sempel ha "
"galowyow VoIP ow tevnydhya an protokol SIP."

